org.activebpel.rt.util
Class AeSafelyViewableSet

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.util.AeSafelyViewableSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Collection, java.util.Set
public class AeSafelyViewableSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Set

Implements a Collection wrapper that maintains a safely readable view of an underlying base collection. All methods that modify the collection are synchronized on the base collection, but all methods that merely examine the collection delegate to a copy of the base collection.
